cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with a structured regression model for networks, which involves machine learning and statistical inference techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
